The Washington Suburban Sanitary Commission shall provide any requested information about the comprehensive plan for water supply systems and sewerage systems in each county as to:
Engineering;
Design;
Present and future capacities;
Available service projections;
Fiscal elements; and
Annual revisions of this information.

The Maryland-National Capital Park and Planning Commission shall provide any requested information to each county as to:
Population;
Growth projections;
Planning factors; and
Other developmental standards.
